00:01:21.170 --> 00:01:25.190
And believe it or not this website
actually only took a few hours to

00:01:25.190 --> 00:01:27.760
build over a weekend, that wasn't too bad.

00:01:27.760 --> 00:01:31.320
What helped is that I approached
responsiveness systematically from

00:01:31.320 --> 00:01:34.480
the start instead of
just as an afterthought.

00:01:34.480 --> 00:01:38.660
All this is to say, that thinking
responsively is a huge help for

00:01:38.660 --> 00:01:39.750
